                <p>The redesigned app prioritized billing and support features based on user research findings. We created a comprehensive mobile experience that balanced Frontier's desire to showcase their technology capabilities with users' primary needs for billing transparency and reliable support.</p>
                
                <p>Key solution elements included streamlined billing workflows, enhanced support tracking features, and a cohesive design system that made the app feel modern and trustworthy.</p>
                
